Chart_Query: SELECT      STR_TO_DATE(`Date`, '%d/%m/%Y') AS xAxis,      AVG(`Cost_Efficiency`) AS yAxis,      `Product` AS series  FROM      starhub_data_asset.data_asset_001_pcc  WHERE      STR_TO_DATE(`Date`, '%d/%m/%Y') >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 1 YEAR)  GROUP BY      xAxis, series  ORDER BY      xAxis ASC, series;
